correctness.rationale: Several core items are correctly grounded (PEALD method; precursors DADI/TMGa/DEZ; co‑reactant Ar/O2 plasma; plasma power 1200 W; substrate; dosing/purge times in seconds; supercycle sequence In–Ga–Zn; 10 nm film thickness; 1:1:1 In:Ga:Zn atomic ratio by XPS; device metrics μ=74.5 cm^2/V·s, Vth=5.02 V, Ion/Ioff≈9.8×10^8; bottom‑gate device). However, there are multiple schema violations and factual/traceability issues: 1) Deposition temperature is incorrectly set to 300 °C (this is an anneal step, not the PEALD deposition temperature; the article does not report deposition temperature). 2) Pressure unit violates schema (used Torr; schema allows only https://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MilliM_HG) and the article gives a range 8–10 Torr, not a single value. 3) DosingTime and PurgeTime units violate schema (used SEC; schema requires MilliSEC); values should be converted (e.g., 0.5 s→500 ms, 12 s→12000 ms, 8 s→8000 ms). 4) Subthreshold swing is misrepresented: article reports 0.53 V/dec; schema’s unit is MilliV, so the numeric should be 530 with unit MilliV, not 0.53 MilliV. 5) Many numeric fields are null/None, which violates the schema’s number type and the task requirement of no empty/null values: growthPerCycle.values[*].value.quantityValue.numericValue, thicknessControl.numberofCycles, nucleationPeriod, flowRates numericValues, uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, elementalConcentration.values, roughness.value, filmDensity.value. 6) thicknessControl structure is incorrect: numberofCycles and filmThickness are placed inside growthPerCycle despite additionalProperties: false; numberofCycles should be a sibling of growthPerCycle per schema. 7) reactantSelection carrierGas and purgingGas are populated as "Not Found" (not grounded in the article); similarly several fields use "Not Found" or arbitrary booleans (saturation=false; otherAspects.filmStability=false; reproducibility=false) without support in the text. 8) supercycleDesign.numberofSubcycles counts are None (invalid) and not grounded; if the 1:1:1 supercycle is intended, counts should be numeric (e.g., 1,1,1) or omitted if not reported. To improve: correct deposition temperature (or omit if unknown), fix units to schema (pressure MilliM_HG; times MilliSEC; SS to 530 MilliV), remove unsupported assumptions, restructure thicknessControl per schema, and replace nulls with valid, grounded numbers or omit non‑required properties.

completeness.rationale: Major completeness and schema issues. (1) Multiple processes not extracted: the article reports several distinct IGZO depositions/compositions (In 10/30/60%, Ga 10/30/60%, and a best device at In:Ga:Zn = 1:1:1), but only a single process is provided. Each composition should be a separate process instance with its own ALD supercycle parameters and device metrics (Table 1 and Fig. 4). (2) Many required fields are left as placeholders or null, violating the schema and the no-null rule: carrierGas, purgingGas, reactor name/manufacturer, thicknessControl.growthPerCycle.values[*].value.quantityValue.numericValue, numberofCycles, nucleationPeriod, flowRates[*].(precursorFlow/coReactantFlow/purgingGasFlow).quantityValue.numericValue, materialProperties.uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values.quantityValue.numericValue, opticalProperties (refractiveIndex, absorptionCoefficient, bandGap), electricalProperties (resistivity, carrierDensity, mobility), roughness.value, filmDensity.value, and many characterizationMethod fields. (3) Unit/schema noncompliance: dosingTime/purgeTime units use SEC but schema requires MilliSEC; pressure unit uses Torr but schema enumerates MilliM_HG; subthresholdSwing uses unit MilliV with value 0.53, whereas the article gives 0.53 V/dec — this should be 530 mV to be both traceable and schema-compliant. (4) Factual misassignment: temperature 300 °C is the annealing step, not the ALD deposition temperature (not reported); pressure is given as 8–10 Torr in the article, but extraction fixes it at 8.0 and in the wrong unit; saturation set to False without evidence; otherAspects.filmStability and reproducibility set to False without support. (5) Supercycle design incomplete: numberofSubcycles.count for In/Ga/Zn is None; the n1:n2:n3 used to realize the compositions (especially 1:1:1) are not provided. (6) Inconsistent/duplicate structuring: filmThickness appears both inside growthPerCycle and again at thicknessControl level. To improve completeness, add separate process entries for each composition studied; fill all required numeric fields with valid values or omit non-required ones; correct all units to schema-allowed QUDT units and adjust magnitudes (e.g., SS in mV); provide carrier/purging gases if stated (likely Ar, but not explicitly given), correct deposition temperature or mark as not reported, include supercycle counts (n1, n2, n3) and total cycles if available, and ensure all values are traceable to the text.
